WEBVTT

00:01:22.599 --> 00:01:23.400
Lu Chengwen

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:25.280
You stay.

00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:29.000
It has nothing to do with me!

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:40.640
Darn it.

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:41.799
That look just now...

00:01:41.799 --> 00:01:43.879
She definitely wants to eat me alive.

00:01:44.200 --> 00:01:46.200
Who did I even offend?

00:01:46.519 --> 00:01:48.079
Xu Xuejiao, you're going to get me killed!

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:57.840
Did you know something just now?

00:01:58.599 --> 00:01:59.239
Ah?

00:01:59.719 --> 00:02:00.480
I what?

00:02:00.480 --> 00:02:01.400
I don't know!

00:02:01.599 --> 00:02:02.599
I know absolutely nothing.

00:02:02.840 --> 00:02:04.319
I was just passing by.

00:02:04.799 --> 00:02:05.400
Hey.

00:02:05.439 --> 00:02:06.599
Dr. Xu's...

00:02:06.599 --> 00:02:07.680
medical skills are incredible.

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:08.120
I am...

00:02:08.120 --> 00:02:09.240
truly in awe.

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:10.240
Hahaha.

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:11.240
Brother Chengwen.

00:02:12.199 --> 00:02:13.439
It better be so.

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:15.120
About what happened today,

00:02:15.120 --> 00:02:16.680
if you dare breathe a word of it,

00:02:17.319 --> 00:02:19.080
especially

00:02:19.080 --> 00:02:20.719
about my acupuncture,

00:02:25.039 --> 00:02:26.639
I promise

00:02:26.639 --> 00:02:27.240
to make you

00:02:27.240 --> 00:02:28.039
wish

00:02:28.039 --> 00:02:29.000
you

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:29.479
were

00:02:29.479 --> 00:02:30.159
dead.

00:02:34.039 --> 00:02:34.360
Hmm.

00:02:34.439 --> 00:02:35.240
Let's go.

00:02:39.879 --> 00:02:41.800
How on earth did he know?

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:43.439
But he's clearly

00:02:43.439 --> 00:02:45.080
an ignorant playboy.

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:47.680
Has he been Playing the fool all along?

00:02:49.240 --> 00:02:50.039
This guy

00:02:50.039 --> 00:02:51.520
hides it pretty well.

00:02:52.840 --> 00:02:53.840
Interesting.

00:02:59.319 --> 00:03:00.240
Gu Zhantian,

00:03:00.240 --> 00:03:01.680
I don't want to see you right now.

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:02.919
If you know what's good for you,

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:04.039
leave immediately.

00:03:04.080 --> 00:03:04.919
Our engagement,

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:06.400
from this moment on,

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:07.000
is completely,

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:07.639
permanently,

00:03:07.639 --> 00:03:08.520
and entirely annulled.

00:03:09.240 --> 00:03:10.639
Ever since the engagement banquet,

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:13.280
I've felt something was off.

00:03:13.639 --> 00:03:15.800
It feels like something

00:03:15.800 --> 00:03:17.840
has been interfering with my actions.

00:03:18.039 --> 00:03:19.960
As if this world

00:03:19.960 --> 00:03:21.439
wasn't originally like this.

00:03:21.599 --> 00:03:23.479
It must be that Lu Chengwen's doing.

00:03:24.319 --> 00:03:25.919
I think you should have killed him long ago.

00:03:26.240 --> 00:03:28.400
But he hasn't done anything heinous.

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:30.199
In fact,

00:03:30.199 --> 00:03:31.840
he seems to be helping me.

00:03:33.319 --> 00:03:35.639
In this world, anyone who goes against your will

00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:40.520
Darn it all.

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:54.080
In the past,

00:03:54.639 --> 00:03:55.639
at the border, I was

00:03:55.639 --> 00:03:57.039
always successful.

00:03:57.599 --> 00:03:59.639
That's because everyone knew me.

00:04:00.479 --> 00:04:01.360
Now,

00:04:02.159 --> 00:04:03.840
I've come to Haicheng to rest,

00:04:04.240 --> 00:04:06.080
hiding my identity.

00:04:06.680 --> 00:04:07.080
Hmph.

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:09.439
They look down on me

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:11.039
and misunderstand me,

00:04:12.199 --> 00:04:13.400
which is normal.

00:04:15.719 --> 00:04:17.000
Young Master is so broad-minded.

00:04:17.279 --> 00:04:17.920
It makes Xuening

00:04:17.920 --> 00:04:18.879
deeply admire you.

00:04:23.839 --> 00:04:24.759
You actually awakened

00:04:24.759 --> 00:04:25.839
the protagonist Gu Zhantian's

00:04:25.839 --> 00:04:26.639
Self-awareness.

00:04:26.839 --> 00:04:27.639
Lu Chengwen,

00:04:27.800 --> 00:04:29.319
I really didn't misjudge you.

00:04:29.800 --> 00:04:30.399
Ah?

00:04:31.160 --> 00:04:31.879
Self-

00:04:31.879 --> 00:04:32.480
awareness?

00:04:33.439 --> 00:04:34.199
A paper doll

00:04:34.199 --> 00:04:35.000
awakened?

00:04:35.319 --> 00:04:36.600
It was just a fleeting moment.

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:38.839
The Heavenly Dao has already taken his consciousness.

00:04:39.199 --> 00:04:39.800
Heavenly

00:04:39.800 --> 00:04:40.079
Dao?

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:41.680
The Heavenly Dao

00:04:41.680 --> 00:04:43.000
is the god of this world.

00:04:43.240 --> 00:04:44.839
It decides the fate of every character.

00:04:45.439 --> 00:04:46.199
And I

00:04:46.199 --> 00:04:47.480
am here to help

00:04:47.480 --> 00:04:48.839
trampled minor characters like you

00:04:48.839 --> 00:04:49.839
defy the heavens and change your fate,

00:04:49.839 --> 00:04:51.199
escaping the control of the Heavenly Dao.

00:04:51.680 --> 00:04:52.519
So,

00:04:52.519 --> 00:04:53.040
you're called

00:04:53.040 --> 00:04:53.920
Fate-Defier

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:55.000
just to

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:56.040
defy the heavens and change fate?

00:04:58.879 --> 00:05:00.319
Why are you looking at me like that?

00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:04.439
Didn't you say

00:05:04.439 --> 00:05:05.279
if I survive until Gu Zhantian

00:05:05.279 --> 00:05:06.079
unifies Haicheng

00:05:06.079 --> 00:05:07.800
and returns to the border for the finale,

00:05:07.800 --> 00:05:09.120
I can go back?

00:05:09.639 --> 00:05:10.720
You're not going to make me help you

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:12.199
fight that Heavenly Dao thing, are you?

00:05:12.879 --> 00:05:13.399
Don't forget

00:05:13.399 --> 00:05:14.279
our deal.

00:05:14.600 --> 00:05:15.839
I extend your life,

00:05:15.920 --> 00:05:17.120
and you work for me.

00:05:17.319 --> 00:05:17.639
No,

00:05:17.639 --> 00:05:18.439
what are you...

00:05:18.480 --> 00:05:19.680
I can't even deal with Gu Zhantian,

00:05:19.680 --> 00:05:20.879
and you want me to help you deal with that

00:05:20.879 --> 00:05:21.519
Heavenly Dao?

00:05:21.519 --> 00:05:22.920
Are you kidding me?

00:05:23.199 --> 00:05:24.199
You have no choice.

00:05:24.319 --> 00:05:25.879
If I am destroyed by the Heavenly Dao,

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:27.319
you will also turn to ashes.

00:05:28.800 --> 00:05:29.600
Besides,

00:05:29.639 --> 00:05:31.240
look at the bonus for this round.

00:05:31.519 --> 00:05:32.839
It's ten million yuan.

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:35.439
Converted to real-world money, it's...

00:05:35.839 --> 00:05:37.680
She got an extra 10,000 yuan in her account today.

00:05:37.839 --> 00:05:38.920
Her son is back.

00:05:40.839 --> 00:05:41.439
Sister Zhao,

00:05:41.439 --> 00:05:42.439
arrange the treatment.

00:05:42.519 --> 00:05:43.319
Okay.

00:05:44.839 --> 00:05:46.000
If you survive to the end,

00:05:46.439 --> 00:05:48.480
you will get a bonus of ten billion yuan.

00:05:55.319 --> 00:05:56.199
I'm going all out!

00:05:57.199 --> 00:05:58.240
Let's get this over with quickly.

00:05:58.600 --> 00:05:59.519
What's the next level?

00:06:03.279 --> 00:06:04.079
What's going on?

00:06:04.199 --> 00:06:05.120
I didn't expect the Heavenly Dao

00:06:05.120 --> 00:06:06.199
to start investigating so soon.

00:06:06.199 --> 00:06:07.399
I'll give you another item.

00:06:07.399 --> 00:06:08.000
Ah?

00:06:12.399 --> 00:06:15.040
God of War Tours Haicheng.

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:16.920
I can't talk to you anymore.

00:06:16.920 --> 00:06:18.040
For the upcoming plot,

00:06:18.279 --> 00:06:19.600
you're on your own.

00:06:25.439 --> 00:06:26.040
Ah?

00:06:26.839 --> 00:06:27.839
What is this situation?

00:06:35.839 --> 00:06:36.839
Character biographies?

00:06:37.639 --> 00:06:38.720
This only has character introductions,

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:40.040
not the full plot!

00:06:40.319 --> 00:06:41.720
Who knows when this Gu Zhantian

00:06:41.720 --> 00:06:43.120
will pop out and kill me?

00:06:46.120 --> 00:06:46.879
Someone's here.

00:06:47.240 --> 00:06:48.600
It must be Gu Zhantian.

00:06:57.199 --> 00:06:57.480
You...

00:06:57.480 --> 00:06:58.600
Why are you here?

00:06:58.600 --> 00:06:59.399
If I didn't come,

00:06:59.399 --> 00:07:00.439
you'd release that batch of fake drugs

00:07:00.439 --> 00:07:01.600
without a hitch.

00:07:03.240 --> 00:07:04.319
What fake drugs?

00:07:11.199 --> 00:07:11.680
Uh...

00:07:11.680 --> 00:07:13.040
So it was me

00:07:13.040 --> 00:07:14.839
who secretly took this batch's

00:07:14.920 --> 00:07:15.800
precious ingredients

00:07:15.800 --> 00:07:16.399
and replaced them with

00:07:16.399 --> 00:07:17.519
cheap ingredients?

00:07:17.600 --> 00:07:17.920
Uh...

00:07:17.920 --> 00:07:18.680
Causing

00:07:18.680 --> 00:07:19.839
the efficacy to fall short of standards.

00:07:20.279 --> 00:07:21.040
And as for me,

00:07:21.040 --> 00:07:21.439
for the sake of

00:07:21.439 --> 00:07:21.920
profit,

00:07:21.920 --> 00:07:23.439
I firmly refused to destroy them,

00:07:23.639 --> 00:07:25.160
and even plan to use tomorrow's press conference

00:07:25.319 --> 00:07:26.560
to grandly launch this medicine?

00:07:26.800 --> 00:07:27.600
As for this pharmaceutical factory,

00:07:27.600 --> 00:07:29.120
although your Lu family is the major shareholder,

00:07:29.519 --> 00:07:31.079
our Leng family also holds a share.

00:07:31.319 --> 00:07:32.680
If you're blinded by greed

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:34.120
and seeking your own doom, I don't care.

00:07:34.759 --> 00:07:36.360
Just don't drag our Leng family down

00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:37.600
and ruin our reputation.

00:07:42.439 --> 00:07:43.279
Brother Chengwen,

00:07:45.879 --> 00:07:48.279
my family also has shares in this factory.

00:07:48.279 --> 00:07:49.839
Why didn't you discuss this with me?

00:07:50.600 --> 00:07:51.160
Oh my god.

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:52.639
Why is it this witch again?

00:07:54.439 --> 00:07:55.720
Where did she come from?

00:07:55.720 --> 00:07:56.519
Yeah.

00:07:58.000 --> 00:07:59.319
It's only been a few days since the engagement party,

00:07:59.800 --> 00:08:01.199
and he already has a new flame.

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:04.800
Ahaha.

00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:05.199
Well,

00:08:05.240 --> 00:08:06.079
don't misunderstand, everyone.

00:08:06.079 --> 00:08:07.040
I'm not familiar with her.

00:08:08.360 --> 00:08:08.720
Hey,

00:08:08.920 --> 00:08:10.839
yesterday you said I was pretty

00:08:10.920 --> 00:08:12.199
and had a great figure.

00:08:13.079 --> 00:08:13.600
Witch,

00:08:13.600 --> 00:08:15.199
are you addicted to messing with me?

00:08:15.879 --> 00:08:16.680
Lu Chengwen,

00:08:17.079 --> 00:08:18.480
I don't care what relationship you two have.

00:08:18.879 --> 00:08:20.399
Give me a straight answer today.

00:08:20.519 --> 00:08:21.959
What do you plan to do with this batch of medicine?

00:08:22.879 --> 00:08:23.480
Uh...

00:08:23.800 --> 00:08:24.759
This batch of medicine,

00:08:24.759 --> 00:08:26.639
it definitely needs to be destroyed.

00:08:27.040 --> 00:08:27.639
He actually

00:08:27.639 --> 00:08:28.879
has such a conscience?

00:08:29.079 --> 00:08:29.639
But,

00:08:29.959 --> 00:08:31.480
I'm currently dealing with

00:08:31.480 --> 00:08:32.240
Gu Zhantian's two backups pestering me.

00:08:32.320 --> 00:08:33.360
It's too dangerous.

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:35.320
I have to take this opportunity

00:08:35.600 --> 00:08:36.919
to make them stop pestering me.

00:08:37.639 --> 00:08:39.200
How am I pestering him again?

00:08:39.480 --> 00:08:40.679
Trying to shake me off?

00:08:40.840 --> 00:08:41.919
In your dreams!

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:44.240
I still have to use that trick.

00:08:44.519 --> 00:08:45.879
Go back to being the villain.

00:08:50.320 --> 00:08:51.320
I think,

00:08:51.559 --> 00:08:52.600
this batch of medicine,

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:54.600
it won't kill anyone anyway.

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:55.879
Why don't

00:08:55.919 --> 00:08:56.799
we just

00:08:56.799 --> 00:08:57.879
take all the insiders

00:08:57.879 --> 00:08:59.080
and silence them all,

00:08:59.320 --> 00:09:00.399
and then

00:09:01.080 --> 00:09:02.039
let it flow into the market?

00:09:02.159 --> 00:09:02.840
How about that?

00:09:04.799 --> 00:09:05.720
Sounds good!

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:07.120
No way!

00:09:10.639 --> 00:09:12.240
Aren't you a doctor who saves lives?

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:13.600
Is that something you should say?

00:09:14.159 --> 00:09:15.679
I'll listen to whatever Brother Chengwen says.

00:09:15.840 --> 00:09:16.159
Come on,

00:09:16.639 --> 00:09:17.480
two to one.

00:09:17.759 --> 00:09:18.440
Motion passed.

00:09:23.320 --> 00:09:24.200
Okay.

00:09:24.200 --> 00:09:25.039
Xuejiao.

00:09:25.039 --> 00:09:26.039
You're so obedient.

00:09:26.120 --> 00:09:26.639
Good girl.

00:09:28.039 --> 00:09:28.519
Uh...

00:09:28.919 --> 00:09:29.639
President Leng.

00:09:29.759 --> 00:09:31.120
Do you have anything to say?

00:09:31.639 --> 00:09:33.200
You're doing this to make me mad, right?

00:09:33.600 --> 00:09:34.399
Fine.

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:36.000
Since President Lu insists on having his way,

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:37.600
I won't stop you.

00:09:37.879 --> 00:09:39.039
You have to stop me!

00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:39.840
This concerns the Leng family's

00:09:39.840 --> 00:09:41.000
business reputation!

00:09:41.399 --> 00:09:42.759
Since President Lu and Xuejiao

00:09:42.759 --> 00:09:43.679
are so affectionate with each other,

00:09:44.200 --> 00:09:45.440
it's not convenient for me to interrupt.

00:09:45.879 --> 00:09:46.679
However,

00:09:46.799 --> 00:09:48.279
when it comes to drug safety,

00:09:48.600 --> 00:09:49.600
I hope President Lu

00:09:49.600 --> 00:09:50.720
keeps a clear head,

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:52.840
and doesn't lead Dasheng Group

00:09:52.840 --> 00:09:53.799
astray.

00:09:59.039 --> 00:10:00.200
Xuejiao,

00:10:01.240 --> 00:10:02.279
this is medicine.

00:10:02.600 --> 00:10:03.000
Medicine

00:10:03.000 --> 00:10:04.240
is meant to cure diseases and save lives.

00:10:04.519 --> 00:10:05.399
But if there's

00:10:05.399 --> 00:10:06.480
something wrong with the medicine,

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:07.840
it will delay the patients' treatment.

00:10:07.840 --> 00:10:08.399
Do you understand?

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:09.919
I understand.

00:10:10.080 --> 00:10:10.399
Ah.

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:11.000
But

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:12.279
the company can't take a loss.

00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:13.840
If their treatment is delayed,

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:15.120
just consider them unlucky.

00:10:15.720 --> 00:10:16.440
Um,

00:10:16.440 --> 00:10:17.759
where's the factory release letter?

00:10:17.759 --> 00:10:18.240
Come on,

00:10:18.399 --> 00:10:19.440
let's sign it.

00:10:19.679 --> 00:10:20.279
Yeah.

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:27.840
Hurry up and sign.

00:10:27.840 --> 00:10:28.480
Your turn.

00:10:37.399 --> 00:10:37.679
Mom,

00:10:37.679 --> 00:10:38.600
it's time for your medicine.

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:40.000
Son,

00:10:40.039 --> 00:10:41.279
this medicine is out-of-pocket.

00:10:41.279 --> 00:10:42.120
It's too expensive.

00:10:42.279 --> 00:10:43.879
I don't need such expensive medicine.

00:10:45.039 --> 00:10:45.960
It is expensive,

00:10:45.960 --> 00:10:46.840
but it works.

00:10:46.840 --> 00:10:47.639
The doctor said

00:10:47.639 --> 00:10:48.759
if you don't take this medicine in your condition,

00:10:48.759 --> 00:10:50.000
you won't survive.

00:11:02.240 --> 00:11:03.519
Report to the Drug Administration immediately.

00:11:03.600 --> 00:11:04.559
Ask them to send someone

00:11:04.559 --> 00:11:05.919
to supervise the entire destruction process of this batch.

00:11:05.919 --> 00:11:06.399
Yes.

00:11:06.399 --> 00:11:07.200
I'll do it right away.

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:07.600
Hey,

00:11:07.600 --> 00:11:08.080
wait.

00:11:08.080 --> 00:11:08.600
President Lu,

00:11:08.600 --> 00:11:10.519
the cost of this batch alone is 600 million.

00:11:10.519 --> 00:11:11.240
Are you really going to...

00:11:11.240 --> 00:11:12.399
All of you, shut up!

00:11:15.080 --> 00:11:16.240
This is medicine.

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:17.600
It's medicine to save lives!

00:11:17.720 --> 00:11:18.679
Let alone 600 million,

00:11:18.679 --> 00:11:19.679
even if it's 60 billion,

00:11:19.679 --> 00:11:21.200
if it can't leave the factory, it can't!

00:11:22.080 --> 00:11:23.519
Listen to me, all of you.

00:11:23.639 --> 00:11:24.919
If anyone dares to sell this batch,

00:11:24.919 --> 00:11:25.519
even a single pill,

00:11:25.720 --> 00:11:27.399
I'll twist their head off and use it as a chamber pot!

00:11:27.399 --> 00:11:28.240
Do I make myself clear?

00:11:31.799 --> 00:11:33.399
Just as I expected.

00:11:40.200 --> 00:11:40.600
Oh,

00:11:41.159 --> 00:11:42.320
I didn't expect

00:11:42.320 --> 00:11:43.519
the domineering

00:11:43.600 --> 00:11:44.399
and wicked

00:11:44.399 --> 00:11:45.279
Young Master Lu

00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:47.039
to be so principled.

00:11:47.639 --> 00:11:48.399
Xuejiao,

00:11:48.559 --> 00:11:48.840
Hmm?

00:11:49.200 --> 00:11:50.120
Do you have any objections?

00:11:50.200 --> 00:11:51.039
I don't.

00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:52.639
I said

00:11:52.799 --> 00:11:53.600
I'll listen to you,

00:11:53.600 --> 00:11:54.399
Brother Chengwen.

00:11:56.200 --> 00:11:57.000
